# Worker full-round evidence (MANDATORY)

**Law:** `brain-os/enforcement/WORKER_FULL_ROUND_EVIDENCE_ENFORCEMENT_LOCKED_v1.md`  
**Incident:** INCIDENT-007 · INCIDENT-008 (timing playbook) · INCIDENT-006  
**Gate:** `python3 scripts/worker_factory_evidence_gate_v1.py --json`

## Timing (INCIDENT-008 — never block chat)

- One sa ≈ **4–6 min** (CHECK ~90s · ACT ~45s · VERIFY ~150s)
- **Tail** `~/.sina/goal1-worker-batch-latest.log` at **-20 lines** — ignore top-of-file stale `agent` halt
- **Unstick** before start if `WORKER_TURN_OPEN`

## Before any Worker turn

1. Session gate: `python3 scripts/cursor_entry_gate.py --role worker`
2. Factory gate must PASS (recipe on INBOX, no orphan `WORKER_TURN_OPEN`, valid `sa-####` meta)
3. If gate FAIL → **do not implement** — report reason + founder uses Hub **Unstick Worker** / Deliver

## Factory chain (one sa)

`CHECK → ACT (if gap) → VERIFY` — never skip ACT when CHECK reported GAP FOUND.

## End every turn — mandatory block

```text
RECIPE: <REGISTRY title> · <prompts/.../sa-XXXX.md> · <verify cmd>
VALIDATION: validators <PASS/FAIL> · broker <PASS|STALE|FAIL|pending> · roles <check/act/verify ran>
EVIDENCE: receipt <path|pending> · PRIORITY <y/n> · disk delta <one line>
BUILT: <yes: file> OR <no: verify-only closeout> OR <none: CHECK only>
```

```yaml
status: WORKER_ROUND_REPORT
round_type: check | act | verify
sa_focus: sa-XXXX
validate:
  spine: PASS|FAIL
  critical_bugs: N
summary: one line
```

Broker: `goal1_lane_broker.py worker-submit` — **never** claim `broker_ok` if JSON shows `sa_mismatch` or `receipt_on_disk`.

## VERIFY closeout (only path)

```bash
bash scripts/worker_verify_closeout_v1.sh --sa sa-XXXX --evidence "..." [--task-validator validate-foo-v1.sh]
bash scripts/worker_verify_fast_v1.sh   # receipt/broker gates + auto-revert fake done
```

**Never** edit `REGISTRY.json` / prompt front matter `status: done` by hand.

## Forbidden

- Closeout without VERIFY broker PASS when monitor broker = STALE
- `round_type: implement` without mapping to check/act/verify
- Implement on CHECK · ACT work on VERIFY · auto-run while `WORKER_TURN_OPEN`
- Trust receipt file alone (INCIDENT-006)

